Model Training

FraudDNNEncoder class: 3 hidden layers, BatchNorm, ReLU, Dropout, penultimate embedding layer
FocalLoss class with α and γ tunable parameters
Bayesian hyperparameter search (Optuna, 30 trials, optimises PR-AUC)
Full 5-fold loop: baselines → DNN → embedding extraction → XGBoost ensemble
Reproduces Table 1 with mean ± std across folds
Saves model weights per fold to results/models/

