    "# Notebook 3: Model Training\n",
    "**Paper:** A Hybrid Deep Learning and Explainable AI Framework for Real-Time Financial Fraud Detection in Dynamic Environments\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook implements the two-stage hybrid architecture:\n",
    "- **Stage 1 — DNN Encoder:** 3–5 fully connected layers, ReLU, dropout, batch normalisation. Trained with cost-sensitive focal loss.\n",
    "- **Stage 2 — Gradient-Boosted Ensemble:** XGBoost/LightGBM trained on DNN embeddings with Bayesian hyperparameter optimisation.\n",
    "- **Baselines:** Logistic Regression, standalone DNN, standalone XGBoost, Random Forest.\n",
    "- **Cross-validation:** 5 time-stratified folds, all metrics reported as mean ± std."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
